values: i find it amazing the things you can learn when you just take the time to truly watch, observe, and most obviously, when you listen.  it's baffling to me how much more i know than others about relationships and i dont necessarily think its because i have experienced more i think it is just that i took the time to really understand what was happening.....my typical over-analyzing, self i suppose.  its also weird how things work out, its almost like...the people you seek out to be your friends or to have relationships with are ultimately never the people you have successful relationships; however, it is also the person right under your nose, or whom you would never consider, who falls right in your lap.....fucking weird man...fuckin weird...i guess you truely do just never know whats lurkin' around the bend....kinda intriguing isnt it..??
wouldn't be cool to have sex in a roman amphitheater, i mean, with the natural acoustics and all, the screams could be heard for miles....
